Class MdwRpcWebServiceAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.centurylink.mdw.services.process.BaseActivity
      • com.centurylink.mdw.workflow.activity.DefaultActivityImpl
        • com.centurylink.mdw.workflow.adapter.PoolableAdapterBase
          • com.centurylink.mdw.workflow.adapter.http.HttpServiceAdapter
            • com.centurylink.mdw.workflow.adapter.soap.SoapWebServiceAdapter
              • com.centurylink.mdw.workflow.adapter.soap.MdwRpcWebServiceAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AdapterActivity, GeneralActivity, AdapterInvocationError, PoolableAdapter

    @Tracked(value=TRACE)
public class MdwRpcWebServiceAdapter
extends SoapWebServiceAdapter
    Old MDW RPC-style web service adapter that simulates a document-style service by specifying a single operation in it's WSDL that accepts and returns a simple string that's expected to contain an XML payload that corresponds to an externally agreed-on XSD (outside the WSDL).
